    "markdown": "### 52. Speechify (US) — TTS ✓\n\n**Status:** Active. 50M+ consumer users. Apple Design Award 2025.\n\nAPI: **$10/1M chars** (~2,000 min audio). 1,000+ voices, **50+ languages**. ~300ms latency. SSML support. Voice cloning via API. On-premise option. Free tier available. ⚠️ Some reports of API waitlist.",
